about.summary: Assertions for testing the characteristics of orca tables and columns

name: orca_test
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "orca_test" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://github.com/UDST/orca_test/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3107b31578b2f6e45c5e57b8bc45c94bf2d59f3d3ad1d7162bf36537f7209cca

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - numpy >=1.0
    - orca >=1.3.0
    - pandas >=0.12
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - orca_test

about:
  home: https://github.com/UDST/orca_test
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Assertions for testing the characteristics of orca tables and columns

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - smmaurer
    - ngoldenberg
